@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title Sort Command Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant SortCommand
participant RecordList
participant Ui
participant Storage

User -> Resumake: sort
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: SortCommand
Resumake -> SortCommand: execute(list)
SortCommand -> RecordList: sort(by title)
SortCommand -> Ui: show sorted message
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare + write if changed
@enduml
